{
  "verses": [
    {
      "verse_num": "1",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Ascribe to Yahweh, you sons of the mighty, ascribe to Yahweh glory and strength."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "2",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Ascribe to Yahweh the glory due to his name. Worship Yahweh in holy array."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "3",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh’s voice is on the waters. The God of glory thunders, even Yahweh on many waters."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "4",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh’s voice is powerful. Yahweh’s voice is full of majesty."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "5",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh’s voice breaks the cedars. Yes, Yahweh breaks in pieces the cedars of Lebanon."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "6",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "He makes them also to skip like a calf; Lebanon and Sirion like a young, wild ox."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "7",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh’s voice strikes with flashes of lightning."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "8",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh’s voice shakes the wilderness."
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh shakes the wilderness of Kadesh."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "9",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh’s voice makes the deer calve, and strips the forests bare."
        },
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "In his temple everything says,"
        },
        {
          "type": "speech",
          "text": "Glory!",
          "speaker": "Unknown"
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "10",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh sat enthroned at the Flood. Yes, Yahweh sits as King forever."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    },
    {
      "verse_num": "11",
      "segments": [
        {
          "type": "hymnal",
          "text": "Yahweh will give strength to his people. Yahweh will bless his people with peace."
        }
      ],
      "footnotes": [],
      "references": []
    }
  ]
}